cdata.name: ZiftrCoin
cdata.desc: ziftrCOIN (ZRC) is a decentralised, open-source cryptocurrency forked from Bitcoin and launched in February 2015. It is developed by Ziftr, a US-based company that offers various e-commerce solutions, such as a browser add-on and mobile applications. The company's goal is to enable consumers to conduct simple, secure transactions, using ziftrCOINs (as well as several other cryptocurrencies), at their favorite retailers.
